c: 10
v: 93
t: "Nummah israa-iil xaylo meqe dabqal oobisneeh ken hayne, meqe rizqhiy (quusi kinnuk) calaalik yani keenih necee, tokkel usun diini caagidil itta mawannon Nabii Mucammadal zsa oobe Qhuraan keenih amma iyyam fanah, Nabiyow diggah ku Rabbi Qhiyaamah ayro usun diini caagidik itta elle waak suggu iyyeenimil ken fan meklele"